        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-trigger" aria-expanded="false">
            <span class="faq-question">Do you provide estimates?</span>
            <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>Yes! We offer free, no-obligation estimates for all services. Contact us or fill out the form above to request one.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-trigger" aria-expanded="false">
            <span class="faq-question">Are you licensed and insured?</span>
            <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>Absolutely. We're fully licensed, insured, and bonded to protect you and your property.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-trigger" aria-expanded="false">
            <span class="faq-question">What areas do you serve?</span>
            <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>We serve Longmont, Boulder, Niwot, and Berthoud. Contact us to see if your area is covered.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-trigger" aria-expanded="false">
            <span class="faq-question">Can you work on weekends?</span>
            <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>We work Saturday mornings by request. Sunday is our rest day. Contact us to arrange weekend scheduling.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-trigger" aria-expanded="false">
            <span class="faq-question">How do I schedule a service?</span>
            <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
          </button>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            <p>Call us at {{ site.phoneDisplay }}, email {{ site.email }}, or use the contact form above. We respond within 24 hours.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <button class="faq-trigger" aria-expanded="false">
            <span class="faq-question">What payment methods do you accept?</span>
            <span class="faq-icon">+</span>
